summary: Part 2 of my RaceMenu preset series. Livelle Forsworn RaceMenu Preset adds in a RaceMenu preset of a hand-crafted Female Breton with the Forsworn aesthetic.
descriptionHtml:
[b][font=Tahoma][size=5]Overview
[/size][/font][/b]This is a simple mod, and as the name implies, it's just a RaceMenu preset of a Female Breton Forsworn named Livelle.

Livelle is Part 2 of my Racemenu presets. You can find the other ones here on [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/41281005/?tb=mods&pUp=1]My Profile[/url] 

[b][font=Tahoma][size=5]Requirements
[/size][/font][/b][list]
[*][color=#9900ff][url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url] [/color]
[*][color=#9900ff][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url] [/color]
[*][color=#9900ff][url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdoos[/url] [/color]
[*][color=#9900ff][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7887/?]Pretty Face[/url] [/color]
[*][color=#9900ff][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/86208/?]Freckle Mania 2[/url][/color] 
[/list][b][font=Tahoma][size=5]
Installation
[/size][/font][/b]Manual Installation made simple. Simply unzip into your Skyrim directory (not the data folder) and you're good to go.

[size=5][b][font=Tahoma]Updates[/font][/b]
[/size]This mod likely won't need updating, but in the event it does, I'll add to this section
[list]
[*]v1.0 - Mod release

[/list]
